nodes.text: Tulana Tuluith was an individual who died by the Battle of Jakku in 5 ABY. While the Galactic Empire's 204th Imperial Fighter Wing fought a New Republic starfighter wing at the battle, the pilots called out names of their lost comrades over an open comm channel, Tuluith's name being called among them.
Tulana Tuluith was mentioned in the 2021 novel Victory's Price, written by Alexander Freed.
